Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:03.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flonyard is in the middle of a great war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero has been summoned to be the savior of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Earthling, Sink Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first battle of Sir Hero, Sink, who\Ncheerfully agreed to help, begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was perfect, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:10.77,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(1200,0)\pos(486,359)}  「First Battle!」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The... The...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Flonyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:21.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's Royal Representative has summoned a hero!{"the country" is too vague here}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also my first time witnessing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! And that rarely seen hero is now present right before our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:39.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that hero does not know our rules of war, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will everything be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've told him all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Laurent is carefully going over it with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Looks like you've memorized the rules and routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The princess told me about them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were summoned by the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:00.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what was your first impression of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute and caring,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention an amazing princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Sir Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:19.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,advance forward and rendezvous with our vanguard, Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink Izumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reconfirm the rules with you one last time, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, when enemy soldiers attack you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just beat them up as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! What a real hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could defeat a hero, wouldn't we be incredible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go for it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the enemy soldiers get hit by your weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll get knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And once they're KOed, they become pet balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Army soldiers will turn into kitty balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be powerless for a certain amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If your palm touches the opponent's head or back, that knocks them out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because touch outs are kind of dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you get bonus points for touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's very fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what just happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but their attack points are rocketing upward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps there'll be a reversal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like this hero is really extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hero after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.87,Location Names 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,00)\pos(322,439)}Meanwhile, in the City of Kinokawa, Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:00.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, you'll be spending spring \Nbreak with Izumi-kun as usual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in a relationship with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But you're close, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because our parents are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Izumi-kun is kind of cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! He's cute and good at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually kind of childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things that Sink likes are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,athletic games and staff techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only passionate about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:38.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the battlefield comprises of land and mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll also be many unstable places, \Nsuch as drawbridges and movable surfaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be fine even if you fall off, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:09.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really... capable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me try him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the princess's decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but even if a hero wasn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gale Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! I'm the hero who answered the summoning, Sink Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Eclair, the commanding officer of the Imperial Guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that beam just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to the crest attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(775,0)}This is your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the treasure of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the holy sword, Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:28.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll turn into whatever shape you wish it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A staff, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What an obscure weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Its length is just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, let me explain the crest attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The crest lies between Flonyard's land and air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a technique that gathers Flonyard's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you gather Flonyard's power to your crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then you combine it with the power of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:07.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, you can transform it into a kind of power called Ki-Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:12.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do a lot of things with this kind of Ki-Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:17.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you would use it for the \Nmost is definitely the crest attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess says that you are an expert with crest attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she told me to consult you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, activate your own crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest activate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:33.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:40.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use all of your strength and spirit and then solidify the crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Convert Flonyard's power to Ki-Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and release it from your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a crest attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although a crest attack is convenient,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:30.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,soldiers with helmets and armor can easily resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...you become exhausted after firing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...so think before you use it.{lots of ellipses because they are completing each other's sentences}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:01.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here expecting at least something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but, at the end of the day, you're just an underling of the doggie princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leonmitchelli!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying for you to call me Princess so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Leonmitchelli Galette des Rois,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,leader of the Galette Lion Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Knight of Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "your Highness," you rude bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Leonmitchelli has finally showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has arrived on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her precious Douma is still as majestic as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, you're in the way! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,perverted hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're fighting amongst themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And could this hero be unexpectedly stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Leo's precious Douma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving as if they're one!\NThey've broken through the water area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:03.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the biggest barrier is the deadly, slippery, slippy slippy wall section.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Biscotti soldiers are trying their best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a little farther to the final blockade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where the final battle will take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busting through, Douma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we'll let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to disrupt my fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King's Divine Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest techniques can do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo is on a different level!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Leonmitchelli's supreme skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:55.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Explosion of the Lion King's Divine Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:15:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as one stands within its perimeter, there won't be a chance to stand back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The super powerful Crest Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it even enveloped her own allies, sacrifices are sometimes needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was still awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Franboise, confirm it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the hero and the ear drooping puppy dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be finished off so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a little too high? Hey, isn't this just too high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero and the captain were all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:46.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're just sitting ducks for her Highness Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't feel like sharing the credit with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't cooperate, we won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cooperate! With that timing we used just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we won't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.27,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,That was cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my opponents were just a midget and an ear drooping puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's fine to continue like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but still,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like giving special service to \Nthe citizens from both countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness Leo, does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm surrendering right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! Her Highness actually surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:11.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That calls for an additional 350 points for defeating the army leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The winning condition this time is to repress the stronghold,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the battle is not considered finished just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the difference in points is overwhelming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Galette army probably doesn't have a chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We really won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, although there was help from the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll praise you for the fact you landed an attack on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't think you can do so well next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "your Highness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was a bit scary to fight with your Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:55.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Photography group, focus on the ear drooping puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to get a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero has used friendly fire on his own ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:36.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did he break her armor, he also tore her clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll get the upper hand on the invasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, her Highness has officially left the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the next invasion will be something to look forward to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this war has not ended yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the front line, concentrate until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best until the time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we look at the hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a confident fighter, but he looks a little silly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, to the knight Eclair,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks for the nice image!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, if the Galette Army had won,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:45.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they would have held the Galette \Nnative wine celebration in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes on like this, and the Biscotti Army wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:52.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then the right to hold a celebration would belong to Biscotti, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Princess Millhiore of the Frianno Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the celebration this time would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. There will be a banquet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with music and singing in Frianno's music hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess's ability to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is already perfect to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Princess actually knows how to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our princess is a world famous singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,World famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Sir Hero and Eclair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:36.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever the Princess has a meeting or conference with other countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she brings her orchestra and sings all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently we've been at war,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we rarely get to enjoy her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:50.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been some time since we last heard the Princess sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'll agree after listening to the Princess's voice.{there really does need to be 's, not just ', with "princess's"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you flourished in the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to invite you to enjoy the \Nupcoming performance in a special seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:05.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, um, I think I should go back home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get in touch with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Sir Hero, it seems that we'll be able to achieve victory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he will come to my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:25.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he goes back too late, his family will be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A summoned hero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is unable to return to or contact his homeworld.{Aegisub claims this is misspelled, but it's not.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the summoning rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:37.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If a hero is summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he won't be able to return to his homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:44.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why heroes are rarely summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you didn't know about that, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. What kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there must still be a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:52.57,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You fool! Idiot! Perverted Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.80,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I said that was an accident!
